In the Matter of the Estate of Gustav Kadar, Deceased. Dreyfus & Co., Appellant; Nicholas R. Doman, as Administrator of the Estate of Gustav Kadar, Deceased, Respondent.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, with $10 costs.

Concur — Peck, P. J., Breitel, Botein,' Valente and Bergan, JJ. [See ante, p. 654.]
